OL,3,CHorse dies at Cheltenham Festival
OL,4,Cafter sustaining 'fatal injury' in
OL,5,Csecond race
OL,7,FA horse has been put down after
OL,8,Fsustaining a fatal injury on the first
OL,9,Fday of the Cheltenham Festival 2026.
OL,11,FHansard was running in the second race
OL,12,Fof the day, the Singer Arkle Challenge
OL,13,FTrophy Steeple Chase, which is about
OL,14,Ftwo miles long.
OL,16,FThe eight-year-old was trained by Gary
OL,17,Fand Josh Moore and started as a long-
OL,18,Fshot outsider in the Arkle.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
